# Enforcement

No runtime component may assume:

Cloud Access

OpenAI Availability

Internet Connectivity

---

Provider implementations must conform to:

BaseProvider

ProviderRequest

ProviderResponse

---

All new features must work with:

Cloud Models

and

Local Models

unless explicitly documented otherwise.

